Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.88,0:00:04.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Seliane...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.25,0:00:06.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollonius...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.69,0:00:23.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}V 1. dni na svete, pod stromom života,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.30,0:00:29.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}dvaja z nás počuli hlasy veľrýb, odrážajúce sa z diaľky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.64,0:00:35.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}So všetkým, čo sme stratili a všetko, čo sme milovali,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.98,0:00:42.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}čo sme mali v náručí, kam sa to zatúľalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:48.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Odpoveď leží v jantári slnka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.99,0:00:55.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Ak by som ťa nestretla, zničila by som anjela.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:01.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Moja duša posadnutá okamihom nesmrteľnosti,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.00,0:01:04.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}nezraní moje krídla.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.67,0:01:11.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Zrodila som sa, aby som spoznala tento pocit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.35,0:01:17.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Po 1.000 rokov a ešte ďalších 2.000, som ťa ľúbila.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:24.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Po 8.000 rokoch, som ťa ľúbila ešte viac.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.03,0:01:30.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Po ďalších 100.000.000 rokov a ešte ďalších 2.000, ťa budem stále ľúbiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.37,0:01:38.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Od 1. dňa, keď som ťa spoznala, hudba v mojom pekle nikdy neprestala.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:49.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,225)}"12.000 rokov starý ľúbostný list"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:09.73,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toho dňa, pred 10.200 rokmi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:17.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako mraky, ktoré siahajú až do stratosféry,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.05,0:02:21.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,sledovali sme spolu stmievanie...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:24.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...ako výnimočný oblúk v slnečných bodoch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:25.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Č-Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.77,0:02:41.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,My, oddaní láske zeme...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:47.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...a ticho počúvame spomienky...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:51.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...hĺbky oceánu v každej rannej kvapke dažďa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:53.54,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,O čom to hovoríš?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:03:00.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Speváci morí, zhromaždení v žiarivej svätyni hĺbok...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:02.76,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Videli sme ich,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:04.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,a počuli ich modlitby...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:19.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pod stromom života, sme sa oddávali...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:23.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...ozvenám začiatku nového sveta...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:26.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aké... je to žiarivé...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:29.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,O čom to hovoríš?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:32.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Si Ťieňový Anjel, však? Vráť mi Barona!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:38.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Po tom všetkom, tvoje oči ma neodrážajú...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:46.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo, čo sa stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:47.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherubín!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:53.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toma...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:58.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aké je to smutné...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:04:02.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vidieť silného nepriateľa z minulosti takého slabého...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:06.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Skončím to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:27.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Úroveň kvantumu Solárneho Aquariona klesla o 11 bodov!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:29.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nepriateľský vojak Cherubín sa blíži!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:34.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemáme inú možnosť! Otvor dieru v bariére a vtiahni Aquariona!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:38.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nastavujem generátor bariéry. Synchronizujem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:49.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nespomínaš si na nič, čo sa stalo pred 12.000 rokmi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:53.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pamätáš si ho v tomto živote?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:02.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To nemôže byť!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:07.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:08.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Baron... Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:13.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:18.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Baron!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:24.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To som ja, Baron! Žiješ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:25.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:29.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Si to vážne ty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:32.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra áno! Som na palube tohto stroja!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:36.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:39.88,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ostaň vzadu! Nesmieš sa ku mne priblížiť!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:41.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to do teba vošlo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:45.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ťieňový Anjel hovoril, že táto vec je bomba!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:47.96,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak sa piblížiš, vybuchne!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:49.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:51.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aké odporné! Bastardi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:52.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Do kelu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:04.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Generátor bariéry sa preťažuje!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:06.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zaťaženie je väčšie ako 75%.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:09.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo! Neblázni!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.71,0:06:14.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň, Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:18.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Viem, že znamená pre teba veľa, ale ak zničíš bariéru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:20.26,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zmĺkni! Pustite ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:23.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedz niečo, Pierre!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:33.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Niekedy je čas, keď sa človek musí zastať kamaráta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:35.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Spravme to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:36.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Neverím tomu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.47,0:06:40.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierre...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:00.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie! Prinesieš nešťastie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:02.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bezkrídli sú hlúpi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:05.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Povolali svoju vlastnú skazu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:07.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Baron, si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:11.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty hlupák! Mal si ma tam nechať!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:14.54,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To nemôžem! Sme priatelia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:15.88,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo... Ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:19.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môj drahý priateľ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:20.88,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ostaň vzadu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:27.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Poď! Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:32.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Baron...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:33.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:35.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Spravil si to pre mňa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:41.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Preč!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:45.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo, staraj sa o deti!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:08:00.26,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bariéra je preč.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:02.26,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:07.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten bastard Apollo vystavil ľudstvo nebezpečenstvu, len kvôli jednej osobe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:11.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto by sa nikdy nestalo, keby bol Sirius na palube!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:13.17,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo, ty idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:14.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo teraz?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:18.26,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetkých môžu zabiť Ťieňoví Anjeli.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:22.94,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Deava nepotrebuje nikoho, kto nemá súcit s priateľmi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:24.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz môžeš odísť!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:54.54,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo! Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:00.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:03.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Na čo čakáš, Apollo! Vstaň!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:05.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pre tvojho priateľa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:08.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si, ak nemôžeš na nich zaútočiť...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:11.26,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...so zlosťou a bolesťou zo straty priateľa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:15.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto sme dostali silu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:17.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silu Aquariona!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:21.49,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:29.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Porazím ich!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:35.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Porucha Aquariona!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:39.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Energické jadro vypúšťa nenormálne množstvo energie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:40.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:43.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozri! Aquarion plače.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.89,0:10:20.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hnusné...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:22.76,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Otoha, nechám ostatok na tebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:23.96,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toma...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:27.20,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môj boj príde neskôr...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:30.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz je čas položiť neopätované city k odpočinku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:34.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:35.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toma?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:37.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toma...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toma... jediný...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:45.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Z pred 12.000 rokov?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:09.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:12.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,"Poplach, votrelec Ťieňový Anjel"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:13.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,"Poplach, votrelec Ťieňový Anjel" Zistený Ťieňový Anjel! Zistený Ťieňový Anjel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:15.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zistený Ťieňový Anjel! Zistený Ťieňový Anjel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:20.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Votrelec Ťieňový Anjel! Výskumné stredisko pod útokom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:21.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:26.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:32.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:34.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:39.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Elementy Sol a Luna boli vyhodené!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:41.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Núdzový level červený!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:43.54,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nech sa každá sekcia evakuuje!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:48.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika, Tsugumi... zoberte miesto namiesto Apolla a Silvie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:49.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Veliteľ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:55.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžeme sa teleportovať, lebo elementy nie sú na palube!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:57.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto som povedal "zoberte."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:00.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, pane!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.33,0:12:03.83,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zistený Ťieňový Anjel! Zistený Ťieňový Anjel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:05.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetky sekcie núdzového opatrenia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:07.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:10.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ťieňový Anjel... je tu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:15.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:53.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ešte si neporozumel, čo si.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:58.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Mal si sa znovu zrodiť v inom tele.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:13:01.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chceš umrieť takto?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:03.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ťieňový Anjel! Priprav sa na koniec!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:15.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Opovažuješ sa ukazovať na mňa mečom...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:17.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie si obyčajný bezkrídly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:24.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:36.26,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Systémy lietania poškodené...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:38.96,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zbrane oddelené a nepoužiteľné.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:40.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako to vyzerá, Tsugumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:41.93,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Poškodenie je ťažké!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.93,0:13:44.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je úžasné, že Apollo a ostatní boli schopní  po tom všetkom bojovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:46.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako je na tom jadro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:48.27,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kryštál energie je stále v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:51.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre, Tsugumi, podel sa o svoju silu so mnou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:54.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre, Sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.38,0:13:55.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To je duch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:58.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika, nezabúdaj, že nemôžeme lietať!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:01.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoberiem si Sol, tak potrebujem aby si ma kryl, Pierre.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:02.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zobrať?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:08.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tieto vibrácie...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:11.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:12.49,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toma?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:17.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten, kto chytil Apolloniusa a Seliane pred 12.000 rokmi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.03,0:14:18.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:22.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Som rád, že si niekto spomína.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:26.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako by som mohol zabudnúť? Je jedno koľkokrát sa znovu zrodím!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:31.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia! Sirius!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:32.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:33.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:38.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty bastard! Čo si spravil Silvii a Siriusovi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:50.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:54.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Blázon. Stále chceš bojovať?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:58.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zmĺkni! Som blázon až do špiku kostí!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:14:59.83,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:03.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Taký hlupák ako ty,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:06.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,musel byť smutný zo straty svojho priateľa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:10.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo, staraj sa o deti...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:13.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Baron...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:18.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak si tak praješ, môžem priviesť tvojho priateľa späť.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:19.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:25.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj keď nemôžeme vytvoriť nový život.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:29.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako obete, mi daj životy týchto dvoch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.87,0:15:31.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dať?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:38.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak ich dám nášmu stromu života, tvoj priateľ bude späť.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:43.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.55,0:15:48.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dovoľ, aby som ti to povedal tak, aby si tomu rozumel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:50.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedz mi len jedno...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:52.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dám ti ich."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:01.76,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Takú vec by som nikdy nemohol povedať!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:06.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj keď si spoznal ich pravú povahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:07.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pravú povahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:26.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to je?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:29.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Majú rovnakú krv.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:31.27,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:35.94,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pravdepodobne vzdialený potomok zradca Apolloniusa,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:37.96,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,a bezkrídla Seliane.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:45.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pravda. Sú rovnakí ako my.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:46.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To nemôže byť!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:51.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie sú ľudia. Prečo váhaš nad ich obetovaním?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:55.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nepozeraj sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.06,0:16:58.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Oni sú...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:00.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Oni sú...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:04.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,moji priatelia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:07.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nebudem robiť, čo hovoríš!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:10.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:11.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:17.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak budeš obeť ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:23.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierre, kry nás!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:24.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.99,0:17:27.49,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Spravíme to, Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:28.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:37.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierre!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:39.83,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Na ceste!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:41.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prichádzam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:46.51,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Už to neudržím!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.51,0:17:48.20,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vydrž, Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:51.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Soluna!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.81,0:17:52.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Soluna?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:58.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zaplatíš, Ťieňový Anjel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.52,0:18:01.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tento pocit... Aký zaujímavý.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:02.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prichádza!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:08.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierre!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:09.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:12.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.51,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Priprav sa na smrť!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:31.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Moc pomalá!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:42.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierre! Tsugumi! Skončíme to s ňou!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:45.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Traja ako jeden! Ohnivý výbuch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:48.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre! Páľ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:50.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bojím sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:52.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz, Tsugumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:53.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.91,0:18:58.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to je?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:18.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ešte sa stretneme.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:19.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:23.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:30.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:33.88,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideme domov... do Atlandie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:35.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Stačí ti to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, je to v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:41.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak to spravilo pierko,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:45.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,môžeme byť schopní odvrátiť skazu Atlandie...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:49.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale teraz, je to jedno.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:59.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz si sa obetoval, namiesto jeho záchrany.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.64,0:20:04.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Urobil si to... aby si ukázal svoje city Slnečnému Krídlu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:06.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vedela si, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:09.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto hovorí...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:12.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto si sa uhla ich útoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:15.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:19.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...ťa ľúbim.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:29.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:36.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto, ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:39.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:45.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak chceš zmieniť niečo o našich pierkach,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.19,0:20:47.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,tak to povedz...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:01.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To nie si ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:06.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo, to čo sa stalo predtým...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:16.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zabudni na to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:19.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to trochu rozbité, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:21.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale jej krídlo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.72,0:21:27.02,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Krídla alebo nie, ty si ty. Na tom záleží.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:30.73,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:32.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie ako ja, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:34.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.07,0:21:38.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto sa ti viac páči?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.57,0:21:40.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakoniec.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.09,0:21:53.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.10,0:22:05.26,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.70,0:23:45.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie! Povedz, že to nie je tak!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.37,0:23:46.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Seliane!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.87,0:23:50.54,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zástupca veliteľa Jerome nemôže byť reinkarnáciou Apolloniusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.54,0:23:52.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Idem, Seliane!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.04,0:23:55.88,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nabudúce v Aquarionovi: "Žiariace tiene"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.00,0:24:00.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(20,0)\pos(454,390)}"Žiariace tiene"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.88,0:23:57.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Neverte recenzii.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.81,0:23:59.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,
